==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[-ivus]]''

===Suffix===
'''-ive'''
# An adjective [[suffix]] signifying [[relating]] or [[belong]]ing to, of the [[nature]] of, [[tend]]ing to; as [[affirmative]], [[active]], [[conclusive]], [[corrective]], [[diminutive]].

===Translations===
*French: [[-if]] ''m'', -ive ''f''
*Italian: [[-ivo]] ''m'', [[-iva]] ''f''
*Romanian: [[-iv]] ''m'', [[-ivă]] ''f''
*Spanish: [[-ivo]] ''m'', [[-iva]] ''f''

